告诉我们吧。

301
00:12:21,280 --> 00:12:22,280
Our website is EnglishPod.com.
我们的网站是EnglishPod.com。

302
00:12:22,280 --> 00:12:23,960
That's all we've got for today, so until next time.
今天的内容就这些，下次再见。

303
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:24,960
